     <profileDesc>
        <abstract><p>A bill of exchange (hundi) drawn by
               <persName ref="#mansaramSuratram">Mansaram Suratram</persName>
                on
               <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">Bakhtawarmal Rekhchand</persName>
                for the payment of 30,000 rupees from the kingdom of
               <placeName ref="#jaipur">Jaipur</placeName>
                to the military camp of the Maratha ruler
               <persName ref="#daulatRaoShinde">Daulat Rao Shinde</persName>
               .<note> Images of the document are published in <ref type="bibl" target="#bahuraSingh1989">Bahura and Singh</ref>, and free to view in <ref type="bibl" target="#shahnawaz2021">an article by Mohammad Shahnawaz</ref>
                  (Open Access), whose transcription and translation are reproduced here with
                  permission. There are minor adjustments to the transcription style to match the
                  style of this website. </note></p></abstract>       
