  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="raj" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>श्री राम जी</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>Shri Ram Ji</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="raj" type="authorisation" rend="top right margin">
            <p>
               <lb rend="empty"/><choice><abbr>दा</abbr><expan>दस्तख़त</expan></choice> <persName ref="#sanwaldas">सावलदास</persName> का होड़ी सी-
               <lb rend="empty"/>कार दाम दीजो
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               Signature of <persName ref="#sanwaldas">Sanwaldas</persName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref>
               to be paid
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="raj" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>सिध श्री लसकर श्रीमंत <persName ref="#daulatRaoShinde">दौलतराव</persName> जी का
               <lb/>सुभसुथानेक सरव वोपमां पत्री भाइ <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">बख्ता-
               <lb/>वरमल रेखचंद</persName> जोग <placeName ref="#jaipur">सवाइी जैपुर</placeName> सुं <persName ref="#mansaramSuratram">मनसा-
               <lb/>राम सूरतराम</persName> केन जै गोपाल वंचीजो अप-
               <lb/>रंची हंडी १ तुमारै ऊपर करी <choice><abbr>रु</abbr><expan>रुपिया</expan></choice> <measure type="currency" unit="rupees" quantity="30000">३००००)</measure> अंकङे तीस
               <lb/>हजार नीमङ़े पंदरा हजार का दुणा अठै राखा
               <lb/>समसथान <placeName ref="#jaipur">सवाइी जैपुर</placeName> की सीरकार का
               <lb/>मुदत हंडी पहुंचा दीन २५ अंक पचीस पाछे सा-
               <lb/>ह जोग हंडी की चलण का ठाव देख चोकस कर
               <lb/>दाम दीजो मीती <date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">चत सुद १३ तरस <choice><abbr>सं</abbr><expan>संवत</expan></choice> १८६७ सड़सठ</date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>Success to the army camp of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_shrimant">Shrimant</ref>
               <persName ref="#daulatRaoShinde">Daulat Rao</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref>,
               <lb/>pleasant and prosperous place, the abode of merit! Therein to <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_bhai">Bhai</ref>
               <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">Bakhta-
                  <lb/>warmal Rekhchand</persName>
                written from
               <placeName ref="#jaipur">Sawai Jaipur</placeName>
                by
               <persName ref="#mansaramSuratram">Mansa-
                  <lb/>ram Suratram</persName>
                whose greetings<note>Literally: victory to <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_gopal">Gopal</ref>.</note> you be pleased to accept. Further,
               <lb/>a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref> is drawn upon you: for
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupees" quantity="30000">Rupees 30,000</measure>
               , in words thirty-
               <lb/>thousand, twice of rupees fifteen thousand, on behalf of
               <lb/>the place, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref><note>Here,
                  the term sarkar refers to state or government.</note> of
               <placeName ref="#jaipur">Sawai Jaipur</placeName>
               ,
               <lb/>a fixed-term <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref><note>This type
                  of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref>, known as a muddati hundi,
                  could only be paid out after the stipulated time period had passed.</note> [of the
               period] 25 days, in words twenty-five, after [which] date,
               <lb/>you will please pay the amount thereof in the current coin to the presenter
               after ascertaining his respectability, title, and address.
               <lb/>Date
               <date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">Chaitra Sudi 13 thirteen, Vikram Samvat 1867
                  sixty-seven</date>
               . </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="raj" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>हुंडी सही राव श्री
               <lb/><persName ref="#bapujiNimbalkar">बापु जी निमालकर</persName> का ज्म
               <lb/><date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">जठ वूद ३</date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>
               <lb/>An authentic <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref>, Rao Shri
               <lb/><persName ref="#bapujiNimbalkar">Bapuji Nimbalkar</persName> received,
               <lb/><date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">Jyeshth Badi 3</date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="mar" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle">
            <p>
               सदर हु हुंडी चे रूपये <persName ref="#bapujiNimbalkar">बापुजी निंबलकर</persName> भरून पावलो हे सही
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p>
               I, <persName ref="#bapujiNimbalkar">Bapuji Nimbalkar</persName>, received payment of the rupees of the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hundi">hundi</ref>, so declared.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="raj" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle">
            <p>
               <lb rend="empty"/><measure type="currency" unit="rupees" quantity="30000">३००००)</measure>
               <lb rend="empty"/>अंकङे तीस हजार न्मन्मङ साढ़ा सात हजार का चौगणा
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6">
            <p><lb rend="empty"/><measure type="currency" unit="rupees" quantity="30000">30,000</measure>/-<note>This number is written inside a small box.</note>
               <lb rend="empty"/>In words, thirty thousand, four times of seven and half thousand<note>This line is written on a diagonal slant.</note></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="raj" type="laterAddition" rend="bottom left">
            <p><num>۲۸</num>/<num>۹۴۸</num> ९४७</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div7" corresp="#orig_div7">
            <p>28/947 947<note>These are accession numbers, written in both Perso-Arabic and Devanagari scripts.</note></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div8" xml:lang="raj" type="clericalNotes" rend="bottom">
            <p>पत्री भाइी <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">बखतावरमल रेखचंद</persName> जोग</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div8" corresp="#orig_div8">
            <p>The letter,<note>The word 'patri', typically letter, may also denote a caste affiliation or official post here, such as patwari or record-keeper. It also occurs before <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">Bakhtawarmal Rekhchand's</persName> name in the main text.</note> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_bhai">Bhai</ref> <persName ref="#bakhtawarmalRekhchand">Bakhtawarmal Rekhchand</persName></p>
         </div>
      </body>
